      "id": "https://uofa.net/synth/validation/morrison-cpb-val-result-001",
      "type": "ValidationResult",
      "name": "CFD vs. experimental hemolysis index comparison — 5 operating points",
      "description": "Relative hemolysis index (RH) computed from CFD was compared against in-vitro measurements at 5 flow-speed operating points. All RH values remained below 1.0, satisfying the acceptance criterion. Maximum observed RH was 0.87 at 4 L/min / 3500 RPM."
    },
    {
      "id": "https://uofa.net/synth/validation/morrison-cpb-val-result-002",
