      "description": "Three mesh densities (2.1 M, 5.4 M, 11.2 M cells) were evaluated. Hemolysis index varied by less than 3.2% between the medium and fine meshes, confirming discretization error is within acceptable bounds for MRL 2."
    }
  ],
