      "rationale": "At MRL 2 this factor is not required to be formally assessed beyond confirming solver convergence monitoring is active. Residual logs confirm convergence to 1e-6 for all simulations; factor scoped to Gradation 1 and satisfied by standard practice."
    },
    {
