      "rationale": "CFD boundary conditions were set to match experimentally measured values: inlet flow rate ±0.05 L/min, rotational speed ±10 RPM, fluid temperature ±0.5°C. Parameter equivalency confirmed by direct comparison of simulation inputs against experimental logs. Formal equivalency metric not required at MRL 2."
